Heureka's learning materials also include the workshop <a href="https://www.heureka.fi/blogs/oppimateriaalit/tekoalylajittelija-arduinolla-75-90-min">Tekoalylajittelija Arduinolla</a>. The page metadata describes it as a <strong>75-90 minute</strong> workshop intended especially for <strong>lower secondary</strong> and <strong>upper secondary</strong> learners.
{% endset %}
{% include "blocks/kadence/advancedheading.njk" %}

<p>According to Heureka, the workshop can be used before a visit, after a visit, or as a standalone activity. That makes it a strong example of how the consortium's themes continue in practice through science centre pedagogy and hands-on AI learning.</p>

